section.section:
The Fund consists of:
money appropriated by the State for rental housing programs, including the Elderly Rental Housing Program under § 4-402 of this title, the Multifamily Rehabilitation Program under § 4-906(b) of this title, the Nonprofit Rehabilitation Program under § 4-929 of this title, and the Rental Housing Production Program under § 4-1502 of this title;
repayments and prepayments of loans made under the programs set forth in item (i) of this paragraph;
money appropriated under § 4-501(c) of this subtitle;
money transferred to the Fund in accordance with §§ 4-502(e), 4-503(d), and 4-505(h) of this subtitle and §§ 3-203(i) and 6-310(g) of this article; and
investment earnings of the Fund.
